## Animation Patterns

### Framer Motion Strategy

#### 1. **Scroll-Triggered Animations**

Use `useInView` hook for viewport-triggered animations:

```javascript
const sectionRef = useRef(null);
const isInView = useInView(sectionRef, { 
  once: true,        // Only animate once
  margin: "-100px"   // Trigger before fully visible
});

<motion.div
  ref={sectionRef}
  initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 30 }}
  animate={isInView ? { opacity: 1, y: 0 } : {}}
  transition={{ duration: 0.6 }}
>
```

#### 2. **Staggered Children**

Animate lists with sequential delays:

```javascript
<motion.div
  variants={staggerContainer}
  initial="hidden"
  whileInView="visible"
  viewport={{ once: true }}
>
  {items.map((item, i) => (
    <motion.div
      key={i}
      variants={childVariants}
    >
      {item}
    </motion.div>
  ))}
</motion.div>

const staggerContainer = {
  visible: {
    transition: {
      staggerChildren: 0.1  // 100ms between each child
    }
  }
};
```

#### 3. **Hover Interactions**

Subtle lift and scale effects:

```javascript
<motion.div
  whileHover={{ y: -4, scale: 1.02 }}
  transition={{ duration: 0.3 }}
>
```

#### 4. **Scroll-Linked Transformations**

Connect animations directly to scroll position:

```javascript
const { scrollYProgress } = useScroll({
  target: containerRef,
  offset: ["start start", "end start"]
});

const scale = useTransform(scrollYProgress, [0, 0.5], [1.3, 1.0]);
const opacity = useTransform(scrollYProgress, [0.15, 0.25], [1, 0]);

<motion.div style={{ scale, opacity }}>
```

### Performance Optimization

**Only animate GPU-accelerated properties**:
- ✅ `opacity`
- ✅ `transform` (translate, scale, rotate)
- ❌ `width`, `height`, `top`, `left`, `margin`

**Custom Easing**:
```javascript
transition={{ 
  duration: 0.6,
  ease: [0.22, 1, 0.36, 1]  // Custom cubic-bezier
}}
```

### Animation Timing Guidelines

| Animation Type | Duration | Easing |
|---------------|----------|--------|
| **Fade In** | 0.5-0.6s | `easeOut` |
| **Slide In** | 0.6-0.8s | `[0.22, 1, 0.36, 1]` |
| **Hover** | 0.2-0.3s | `easeInOut` |
| **Button Click** | 0.15s | `easeOut` |
| **Page Transition** | 0.4s | `easeInOut` |

